3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper discusses a logic that can handle uncertainty and possibility, which are important concepts in machine learning. 
4. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper's focus on possibility theory and its application to automated deduction may have implications for cryptography and security. 
5. cs.PL (Programming Languages) - The paper's discussion of automated deduction and resolution principles may be relevant to programming languages research.
